    "en": {
      "title": "Indictment against Kehaliya",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Bribery and Corruption Eradication Commission has filed a charge sheet in the High Court against three persons including Minister Kehaliya Rambukwella for illegally purchasing GL pipes when he was the Minister of Health.",
        "During the presidential election in 2015, it has been alleged against Kehaliya and others that 9 lakh 90 thousand rupees have been lost due to the 600 pipes purchased using the funds of the Sri Lanka Rupee Corporation."
      ],
